						<h3>Mentoring and Committee Work</h3>
						<ul>
							<li>Supervised undergraduate, master, and doctoral students at Peking University and Wuhan University</li>
							<li>Session Chair, Fresh Blood for Freshwater 2025, HUN-REN Institute of Aquatic Ecology, Hungary</li>
							<li>Technical consulting for ESGreenChina LLC. and DataSea Inc.</li>
							<li>Life Member, European Geosciences Union (since 2021)</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>
